trans-unit.source: Represents a converter that converts the dimensions of a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"></xref> control into a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et konverteringsprogram som konverterer mål for en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"> </xref> kontrollere til en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush> created by this converter applies an <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OpacityMask%2A> to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Border> of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> so that it does not appear in the area defined for the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush>opprettet av denne konverteringsprogram gjelder en <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OpacityMask%2A>til den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Border>av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>slik at den ikke finnes i området som er definert for den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Border> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement.OpacityMask%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.BorderGapMaskConverter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.BorderGapMaskConverter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"></xref> that draws the border for a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush"> </xref> som tegner kantlinje for en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The three numbers that are in the `values` parameter represent the following <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> control parameters: - The width of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> content.
trans-unit.target: De tre tallene i den `values` parameteren representere følgende <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>kontrollerer parametere:-bredden på de <xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A>innhold.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox>

trans-unit.target: En matrise med tre tall som representerer den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"> </xref> kontrollerer parametere.

trans-unit.source: The width of the visible line to the left of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.HeaderedContentControl.Header*> in the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.GroupBox"></xref>.
